; Trace level should control verbosity of trace output.
; At level 0, no [TRACE] messages should appear.
; At level 1, only high-level trace messages appear.
; At level 2, detailed per-transaction breakdowns also appear.
2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal --trace 0 2>/dev/null
             $-10.00  Assets:Cash
              $10.00  Expenses:Food
--------------------
                   0
end test

test bal --trace 1 2>/dev/null
             $-10.00  Assets:Cash
              $10.00  Expenses:Food
--------------------
                   0
end test

test bal --trace 2 2>/dev/null
             $-10.00  Assets:Cash
              $10.00  Expenses:Food
--------------------
                   0
end test
